I"$<p>Ultimately, our mood is influenced by many aspects of our lives. It is natural and normal to feel uncomfortable emotions and to be triggered by difficult events in our lives.</p>

<p>Sometimes we may spend longer periods of time feeling low and powerless over how we experience life.</p>

<p>Overcoming depression involves developing an understanding of the areas of our lives that are not serving us, or that are out of balance, so that we can support ourselves to find new ways of experiencing self care, meaning and purpose in our lives.</p>
